---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl
font-bold mb-6 text-center">Das OSI-Modell</h1>
    <table class="border
border-gray-300 max-w-4xl w-full">
      <thead>
        <tr class="bg-gray-200">
          <th class="border px-4 py-2">OSI-Schicht Nr.</th>
          <th class="border px-4 py-2">Name (Englisch)</th>
          <th class="border px-4 py-2">Name (Deutsch)</th>
          <th class="border px-4 py-2">Verwendete Protokolle</th>
          <th class="border px-4
py-2">Verwendete Adressen</th>
          <th class="border px-4 py-2">Mögliche Fehler</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">7</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Application</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Anwendung</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">HTTP, FTP, SMTP</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">N/A</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2"
            >Falsche Datendarstellung, unzureichende Zugriffsrechte</td
          >
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="border
px-4 py-2">6</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Presentation</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Darstellung</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">SSL, TLS, JPEG, ASCII</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">N/A</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Fehlende Datenkonvertierung</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">5</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Session</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Sitzung</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">NetBIOS, RPC</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">N/A</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Abgebrochene Sitzungen</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">4</td>
          <td class="border
px-4 py-2">Transport</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Transport</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">TCP, UDP</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Port-Nummern</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Paketverlust, falsche Segmentierung</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">3</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Network</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Vermittlung</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">IP, ICMP</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">IP-Adressen</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Routing-Fehler, Adressenkonflikte</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">2</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Data Link</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Sicherung</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Ethernet, PPP</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">MAC-Adressen</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Kollisionsfehler, Frame-Verlust</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">1</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Physical</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Bitübertragung</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">Ethernet, USB, WLAN</td>
          <td class="border px-4 py-2">N/A</td>
          <td class="border px-4
py-2">Signalverlust, physische Schäden</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="mt-8 max-w-4xl">
      <strong>Tipp:</strong> Um die Namen der OSI-Schichten in Deutsch zu lernen,
      können Sie diesen Satz verwenden:
      <br />
      <strong>A</strong>lle <strong>d</strong>eutsche
      <strong>S</strong>tudenten <strong>t</strong>rinken
      <strong>v</strong>erschiedene <strong>S</strong>orten
      <strong>B</strong>ier.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
